  acceptancecriteria "ARCHITECTURE.md lists concrete crates, ALN shards, and SQL files that implement the execution-layer role; spine modules expose non-actuating functions that map eco_restoration_shard KER/Lyapunov math into Prometheus-Praxis without duplicating residual logic; references to econetrepoindex and ecoconstellationindex are correctly wired and validated via a small Python/SQL harness."
  notes "Keep spine modules thin, declarative, and governance-first; rely on existing eco_restoration_shard crates and ALN specs instead of introducing new Rust crates."

